      "widgets_values": [
        "\n\nA scruffy terrier and a sleek orange tabby cat are engaged in a fierce scuffle on a sun-dappled park bench at dusk. The dog's matted fur sticks to its damp nose from pawing at the cat's tail, while the cat's claws dig into the terrier's scruff as it attempts to bite the back of its neck. A discarded chew toy lies between them, its frayed strings tangled in the dirt. The dog's ears are pinned back in fury, its breath coming in sharp pants, while the cat's emerald eyes glow with predatory intent as it leaps over the terrier's head for a final, desperate swipe."
